# RSpec / TDD

Read [spec/AGENTS.md](../../spec/AGENTS.md) and [docs/TESTING.md](../../docs/TESTING.md).

- Strict TDD for business behavior; specs in `spec/models/` only unless policy changes.
- Factory Bot only; no YAML fixtures; no `pending` examples.
- Cover validations, uniqueness, callbacks, and data side effects (notifications, etc.).
- No request, view, helper, or system specs.
- Do not run test commands unless explicitly requested.

